https://mailinabox.email/guide.html#setup

To edit the nameserver of a domain name,
1st edit hostnames
ns1.box your mail server ip
ns2.box your mail server ip

then edit your nameserver 
ns1.box.hobbyix.com
ns2.box.hobbyix.com

When we've mail in a box setup.
Open box.hobbyix.com/admin for admin panel
Here go to custom and edit ip of your site.
